Multiple ports:
curl -v http://localhost:8000/ 
curl -v http://localhost:9000/ 
Multiple Hosts: 
curl --resolve example.com:8080:127.0.0.1 http://example.com:8080
Error Page: 
curl -v http://localhost:8000/error
Client Body Size:
curl -X POST -H "Content-Type: plain/text" --data "BODY IS HERE write something shorter or longer than body limi"

Routes to different directories:
curl -v http://localhost:8000/directory
Default file to search in a directory:
curl -v http://localhost:8000/teste2/teste.html
AllowedMethods:
curl -v -X POST -d "data_to_send" http://localhost:8000/  

Basic Get:
curl -v http://localhost:8000/ 
Basic Post:
curl -v -X POST -d "data_to_send" http://localhost:8000/  
Basic Delete:
curl -v -X DELETE http://localhost:8000/
Basic Unknow:
curl -v -X UNKNOWN http://localhost:8000/
Basic Upload:
curl -X POST -H "Content-Type:multipart/form-data" -F "file=@teste.txt" http://localhost:8000/

SIEGE Tests:
siege -b http://localhost:8000